{The following model games are dedicated to the position arising after} 1. e4
c5 2. c3 d5 3. exd5 Qxd5 4. d4 Nf6 5. Nf3 e6 6. Be3 {This is one of the main
and obvious human moves which is quite popular. We will quickly capture on d4
and meet with Bb4+. Make sure to study the model games that follow only after
consulting the theoretical file at the beginning of the lecture.} *

